snippet: Despite Coach Rex Ryan’s bold predictions last summer, after 11 games, the 4-7 Jets rank 19th in defense and 28th in offense.
abstract: Ben Shpigel On Pro Football column notes that despite New York Jets coach Rex Ryan's bold predictions in 2011, Jets rank 19th in defense and 28th in offense after 11 games.
lead_paragraph: Despite Coach Rex Ryan’s bold predictions last summer, after 11 games, the 4-7 Jets rank 19th in defense and 28th in offense.

headline.seo: Rex Ryan’s Tenure With Jets Marked by Unmet Expectations
headline.main: So Far, Ryan’s Great Expectations for the Jets Have Been Fiction
